    "Another shared application is the enhancement of quality control procedures in the food and beverage industry.",
    "Electronic noses (e-noses) and electronic tongues (e-tongues) use sensor arrays to detect olfactory and gustatory signals, respectively.",
    "When integrated with AI, these systems can monitor production processes in real time, identifying deviations in aroma or taste that could affect product consistency.",
    "This ensures high-quality standards and builds consumer trust through reliable sensory performance.",
